plot: At the music video shoot, Nat is confused why the director is attempting to make his song "Catch Up With The End" humorous because that's not how he intended it to be. Rosalina thinks that Alex so funny, and she thinks that stand up comedians are so brave. Because of this, Nat decides to perform at a stand-up comedy club, which initially fails. In the end, Nat and the band perform his song at a night club featuring George Lopez as the opening act.—Anonymous
